                Features of this mod include:

                <ul>
                    <li>Water Bills</li>
                    <li>
                        Adjustable price per liter (can't adjust after game
                        start to avoid cheating the system :3)
                    </li>
                    <li>Adjustable water combustion for bathroom shower</li>
                    <li>
                        Adjustable water combustion for tap in kitchen and
                        bathroom
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/mysummercar/mods/5475">
